Subject: [PATCH] Update to Sisu 0.1.0 and Guice 3.1.6

Sisu depends on Guice, but dependency scope changed from "compile" to
"provided" in Sisu 0.1.0.  As a Sisu user, Maven needs to have runtime
dependency on Guice.
